      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>Led the design of a website aimed at increasing medical insurance awareness among UCI students. Includes resource pages, an easy-to-navigate glossary, and an integrated chatbot for FAQs.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
      <h2>Problem</h2>
      <p>Many students struggle to understand insurance terms and coverage options, leading to confusion and lack of access to healthcare resources.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
      <h2>Process</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Researched common student pain points regarding insurance literacy.</li>
        <li>Designed clear information architecture and intuitive navigation.</li>
        <li>Integrated chatbot and glossary for quick guidance.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mb-5">
      <h2>Outcome</h2>
      <p>The platform improved understanding of insurance concepts and provided an accessible, student-centered resource, supporting informed healthcare decisions.</p>
    </section>

